    <!-- ===== QUESTIONS TO ASK ===== -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">Questions to Ask</div>
      <div style="font-size: 9px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 6px;">Select 2-3 based on conversation flow. These fill gaps in research and deepen the relationship.</div>

      <div class="question-item">
        <span class="question-num">1</span>
        <div>
          <div class="question-text">What does the next 5-10 years look like for you personally and professionally?</div>
          <div class="question-reveals">Reveals: exit timeline, whether he's building to sell or building a legacy firm, personal goals beyond the business</div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="question-item">
        <span class="question-num">2</span>
        <div>
          <div class="question-text">If something happened to you tomorrow, who would run the firm? How would clients be served?</div>
          <div class="question-reveals">Reveals: succession planning gaps, key person dependency, whether he has a documented continuity plan</div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="question-item">
        <span class="question-num">3</span>
        <div>
          <div class="question-text">Are you working with a business attorney and tax advisor on entity structure and exit planning, or is that something you handle internally?</div>
          <div class="question-reveals">Reveals: sophistication of current planning, gaps in advisory team, competitive landscape for our services</div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="question-item">
        <span class="question-num">4</span>
        <div>
          <div class="question-text">What percentage of your net worth is tied up in the business vs liquid investable assets?</div>
          <div class="question-reveals">Reveals: concentrated position risk, diversification needs, whether he's ready for a partial liquidity event</div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="question-item">
        <span class="question-num">5</span>
        <div>
          <div class="question-text">Have you been approached by any PE-backed platforms or larger RIAs about acquisition or partnership?</div>
          <div class="question-reveals">Reveals: market interest in his firm, whether he's thinking about exit, competitive urgency for our engagement</div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

